Start
Float   offer, price      Discount 
String   user_ type  
For all client applies the transaction 
Read offer, price, user_type     
IF (price >=40) THEN
Discount= 20* sales, 
Else 
    Discount= 2* sales 
Print Discount 
End IF
IF user_ type= “old customer” THEN
Discount= 25;
   Print Discount 
End IF 
END For
Print “Over”

